To reproduce, i am doing a goto "lolo, mt" and draw a box around the area.. in my case, i went from the 8 houses on the top left, to the red parking area on the bottom right.. (i am zoomed in pretty far)

Anyways, sometimes it will work randomly, but try again and it will not work again.

It seems to be working with googlesatellitemap
